2. Conduct regular monitoring and analysis of receivable accounts and request for write-off of dormant accounts; and
3. Monitor compliance on the submission of liquidation documents within the prescribed period and grant additional fund assistance only when the previous ones are settled. Also, improve the present monitoring and control measures on the liquidation of fund releases.

